<SYNC Start=1353377><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1354820><P Class=KRCC>
왜 그러세요.
<SYNC Start=1356220><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1357368><P Class=KRCC>
